## 🌐 Phase 8: Deployment & Domain

| Step | Service | Cost |
|------|---------|------|
| **Buy domain** | GoDaddy / Namecheap / Google Domains | ~₹800/year |
| **Host frontend** | Firebase Hosting / Vercel / Netlify | Free |
| **Host backend** | Render / Railway / Firebase Functions | Free tier available |
| **Database** | Firebase Firestore / MongoDB Atlas | Free tier (1GB) |
| **CDN** | Cloudflare (free plan) | Free |
| **SSL** | Included with Firebase/Vercel | Free |

